PN,31501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FNearly 3,000 patients a day are being
OL,8,Fcared for in corridors or makeshift
OL,9,Fareas, NHS England has revealed as
OL,10,Ffigures showing the scale of so-called
OL,11,Fcorridor care have been published for
OL,12,Fthe first time.
OL,14,FThere were an average of 2,241
OL,15,Finstances each day in May of a patient
OL,16,Freceiving 'corridor care' for more
OL,17,Fthan 45 minutes in hospital emergency
OL,18,Fdepartments in England, the figures
OL,19,Fshow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FA further 699 patients received care
OL,8,Fwithin a ward but not within a
OL,9,Fdesignated bed space on average each
OL,10,Fday last month. This is based on a
OL,11,Fsnapshot of patient numbers at 8am
OL,12,Feach morning.
OL,14,FA patient is classed as receiving
OL,15,Fcorridor care if their treatment does
OL,16,Fnot take place in a clinically
OL,17,Fappropriate and safe setting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FThe criteria used for defining an
OL,8,Fappropriate setting include at-bed
OL,9,Fservices such as oxygen and call
OL,10,Fbells; whether privacy can be
OL,11,Fmaintained; access to food, water and
OL,12,Ftoilets; and whether lights can be
OL,13,Fturned off and noise levels minimised
OL,14,Fto allow sleep.
OL,16,FFootage shows dozens of patients
OL,17,Fwaiting for a bed on a ward at the A&E
OL,18,Fdepartment at Queen's Hospital late
OL,19,Flast year
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FThe data includes patients receiving
OL,8,Ftreatment; or waiting for assessment,
OL,9,Fadmission or transfer; but it does not
OL,10,Finclude ambulance handover delays.
OL,12,FIt comes after research by ITV News
OL,13,Frevealed that since 2020, government
OL,14,Fand hospital trusts had received 27
OL,15,Fformal warnings from coroners over
OL,16,Fpotential future deaths related to
OL,17,Fhospital corridor care, overcrowding
OL,18,For lack of beds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FIn a bid to address this issue the
OL,8,Fgovernment said it would start
OL,9,Fcollecting and publishing data on
OL,10,Fcorridor care from May 2026.
OL,12,FHowever, some doctors expressed
OL,13,Fconcerns that the problem will "become
OL,14,Fhidden" as a result, with hospitals
OL,15,Ftaking shortcuts in order to improve
OL,16,Ftheir data.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FEarlier this year an NHS whistleblower
OL,8,Ftold ITV News Health Correspondent
OL,9,FRebecca Barry that patients are "dying
OL,10,Fin corridors" because of a lack of
OL,11,Favailable hospital beds.
OL,13,F"Today I walked through A&E and there
OL,14,Fwere patients upon patients on oxygen
OL,15,Fin the corridors," the unnamed A&E
OL,16,Fworker said. "It's embarrassing to
OL,17,Fwork for the NHS. It's heartbreaking,
OL,18,Fit's depressing.
OL,26,@qD@aOUrD@MO]uD@AOUwD@RO]xD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,F"It's like it's normal - and it's not
OL,8,Fnormal. Patients are dying in
OL,9,Fcorridors, and we're just watching
OL,10,Fpeople die, and there's nothing we can
OL,11,Fdo about it."
OL,13,FOne such case was Roger Bass, 90, who
OL,14,Fdied on a trolley, surrounded by other
OL,15,Fpatients in a crowded corridor of
OL,16,FQueen's Hospital in Romford at the end
OL,17,Fof November after suffering a
OL,18,Fsuspected stroke.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FHis children, Sue and Mike, told ITV
OL,8,FNews the situation at the hospital was
OL,9,F"absolutely disgusting".
OL,11,F"It's shameful. He had no dignity...
OL,12,FHe should've been in a private room
OL,13,Fwhere his family could be around him,
OL,14,Fsaying our prayers and our last
OL,15,Fgoodbyes - not in a corridor," Sue
OL,16,Fsaid in December.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@AOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FThe family of Roger Bass tell ITV News
OL,8,Fin December that he was badly 'let
OL,9,Fdown' by the NHS after he died in a
OL,10,Fbusy hospital corridor ` a death his
OL,11,Ffamily described as 'degrading'
OL,13,FThe Royal College of Emergency
OL,14,FMedicine has called on the government
OL,15,Fto take tougher action to end the
OL,16,F"shameful practice" of corridor care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,F"We cannot wait years for things to
OL,8,Fimprove. Patients and hard-working ED
OL,9,Fstaff have been frustrated by the lack
OL,10,Fof action across the UK, and deserve
OL,11,Fbetter from their health service
OL,12,Fleaders and politicians," college
OL,13,Fpresident Dr Ian Higginson said.
OL,15,FThe NHS waiting list for planned
OL,16,Fhospital treatments in England rose
OL,17,Ffor the first time in six months,
OL,18,Ffigures also show.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FAn estimated 7.22 million treatments
OL,8,Fwere waiting to be carried out at the
OL,9,Fend of April, relating to 6.11 million
OL,10,Fpatients. This is up from 7.11 million
OL,11,Ftreatments and 6.02 million patients
OL,12,Fat the end of March.
OL,14,FThe increase means the size of the
OL,15,Flist has returned to where it stood in
OL,16,FFebruary, reversing the fall that took
OL,17,Fplace in March.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,FSiva Anandaciva, director of policy,
OL,8,Fevents and partnerships at the King's
OL,9,FFund, said: "These figures confirm the
OL,10,Fscale of something that should never
OL,11,Fhave been normalised in the NHS.
OL,13,F"Patients are routinely being treated
OL,14,Fin hospital corridors, without privacy
OL,15,For dignity. Pressure across the whole
OL,16,Fhealth and care system is spilling
OL,17,Finto A&E.
OL,26,@qD@MOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
