PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781280694
OL,3,CNearly 3,000 NHS patients a day
OL,4,Creceive corridor care in England, data
OL,5,Cshows
OL,7,F"The sheer scale of corridor care in
OL,8,Fthe NHS is deeply concerning, equating
OL,9,Fto three in every 100 who attended an
OL,10,Faccident and emergency department
OL,11,Fevery day."
OL,13,FITV News has contacted the Department
OL,14,Fof Health and Social Care (DHSC) for
OL,15,Fcomment.
